{"tid":1386150,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[歡迎討論] 搵公司幫手推動罷工  入黎討論/屌","createTime":"2019-07-30T09:15:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T12:36:12.000Z","uid":284976,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4707b0d5db041f6b8ee895365b929bf6eff7ac8f","tid":1386150,"uid":284976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:15:10.000Z","msg":"之前開過個po但冇人理，呢個idea可能好on9好柒但我諗緊可唔可以叫公司幫手收留罷工既人去推動罷工。歡迎屌同討論。<br />\n<br />\n唔敢罷工既人都係 <span style=\"color: red;\">驚會俾人炒</span> ，所以如果有公司肯出黎話 <span style=\"color: red;\">歡迎罷工既人如果俾人炒就入黎做</span> ，雖然人工未必夠罷工前既人工高，但起碼最壞情況下俾人炒左都仲有份新工， <span style=\"color: red;\">唔會零收入</span> ，因而鼓勵更多人出黎罷工。<br />\n<br />\n咁公司方面如果洗錢請人咪冇錢？所以就要 <span style=\"color: red;\">靠連登仔幫手不停幫襯呢d公司</span> 俾錢佢賺，形成良性循環。<br />\n<br />\n暫時諗到既缺點：<br />\n-可能冇公司會肯幫手<br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家屌同埋提出更好既提議，或者其實根本冇得搞(?) 第一次係連登講建議，希望幫到手。"},{"pid":"13341c52091cba95c5cda42f0088e0b9d92334d2","tid":1386150,"uid":284976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:15:47.000Z","msg":"自推1"},{"pid":"0d255bffb187a2a2e853f7084f16f52fa9c25622","tid":1386150,"uid":284976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:15:57.000Z","msg":"自推2"},{"pid":"ac855a12981c6d23b891f4fab7048f3f615ce4f4","tid":1386150,"uid":284976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:16:08.000Z","msg":"自推3"},{"pid":"6efc32e507c390ec4102cbae1f70b4e0ab4a02c2","tid":1386150,"uid":284976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:16:18.000Z","msg":"自推4"},{"pid":"23bec1f87f076b5badd3b54abb4ffdeacd089756","tid":1386150,"uid":284976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:16:28.000Z","msg":"自推5"},{"pid":"84a4f0e64e6a30fef606f40fe286cc47d8091e23","tid":1386150,"uid":284976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:16:46.000Z","msg":"自推6"},{"pid":"ec09ffecc0b7c2c306d6397fc914929cb157639b","tid":1386150,"uid":149420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c